name: Hugo F. BACCARI et al. v. Donald M. SCHWARTZ

parties: Hugo F. BACCARI et al. v. Donald M. SCHWARTZ.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiffs’ motion to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is assigned to the motion calendar for Wednesday, March 5,1980 at 9:30 a. m. for oral argument.'
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Kirshenbaum Law Offices, Inc., Sanford M. Kirshenbaum, Providence, for plaintiffs.
Samuel A. Olevson, Providence, for defendant.
